18
19class AudioEncoderPcm16B final : public AudioEncoderPcm {
20 public:

27 };

31
32 protected:
33 size_t EncodeCall(const int16_t* audio,
34 size_t input_len,
35 uint8_t* encoded) override;
36
37 size_t BytesPerSample() const override;
38
39 AudioEncoder::CodecType GetCodecType() const override;
40
41 private:
